Brochure for the Data Science Collaboration between INE Chile and PARIS21 Introduction

Brochure for the Data Science Collaboration between INE Chile and PARIS21 Introduction This brochure aims at illustrating the of the collaboration between INE Chile and PARIS21 which took place from September to December 2022. It was initiated thanks to the Data Science Accelerator program organized by the Office of National Statistics (ONS) of the United Kingdom. We are greatful for all the work that was put in by Nicolas Eduardo Guarda Hinostroza (INE Chile), Yu Tian (PARIS21) and Johannes Abele (PARIS21).

1 Background PARIS21 produces the Partner Report on Support to Statistics (PRESS) annually to report on trends in support to statistics. The methodology is applied retrospectively for all previous years to ensure comparability over time. This document presents the methodology.
